      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.21568627630718912,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "唱,它们的歌声欢快而清",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2553784813099871,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.21568627630718912,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "脆,唤醒了沉睡的城市,",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.27810575309029006,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.21568627630718912,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "开始新的一天充满",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3008330248705931,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.15686274640522851,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "希望和",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3008330248705931,
      "left": 0.2745098003267971,
      "width": 0.05882352990196062,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "可能性。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3235602966508962,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.07843137320261427,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "科技的发展正在以前所未",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.35859817397886334,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.21568627630718912,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "有的速度改变我们的生活",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3813254457591663,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.21568627630718912,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "方式和工作模式。每天都",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4040527175394693,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.21568627630718912,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "有新的创新和发明出现,",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4267799893197724,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.21568627630718912,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "从人工智能到可再生能",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4495072611000754,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.1960784330065356,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "源,这些技术进步深",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4722345328803785,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.17647058970588206,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "刻地",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4722345328803785,
