      "width": 0.21568627630718912,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "然屹立不倒。从埃及的金",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6445830105476764,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.21568627630718912,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "字塔到中国的长城,这些",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6673102823279796,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.21568627630718912,
      "height": 0.015151514520201985
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "建筑不仅展示了我们祖先",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6900375541082826,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.21568627630718912,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "的非凡智慧和惊人的创造",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7127648258885856,
